# OBJECT::CONVERT_OLD_PICKUP_TYPE_TO_NEW

## Summary
A temporary command to convert old pickup types to the new hash types

## Parameters
* **PICKUP_TYPE** oldPickupType

## Returns
* **PICKUP_TYPE**
